edge: The character played by Irrfan Khan in the movie is Saajan Fernandes.
Nimrat Kaur portrays the character of Ila Singh in the movie.
Nawazuddin Siddiqui essays the role of Aslam Shaikh in the movie.
Lillete Dubey acts as Ila's mother in the movie.
Nakul Vaid depicts Rajiv Singh in the movie.
Bharati Achrekar portrays the character of Mrs. Deshpande a.k.a. 'Auntie' in the movie (voice only).
Yashvi Puneet Nagar depicts Yashvi Singh in the movie.
Denzil Smith essays the role of Mr. Shroff in the movie.
Shruti Bapna portrays the character of Mehrunissa in the movie.
